@Git Center: 
@1bfqutudhtexlka: 
@Moor: 
I found the problem. It was not the Tor installation. The problem was the Zeronet installation with Ubuntu Snap.
I downloaded now the Zeronet Bundle from Github. After starting this, all was fine, even with Tor.
When I try to use the Snap Zeronet I get the described problem with Tor.
Perhaps somebody should make a workaround with Snap/Zeronet and Tor to fix this.
